 26/12/18 Gourdinn A fine Box Day which was observ by us as a holiday . I made the round of billet and found them fair good save for a lot of tin lie around . Brigad Major came in and join in the inspect . Afternoon we were beaten by the 24th Battalion at footbal . Heard today that 1st and 2nd Divis are to go to Germani accompani by DA 's of other unit but that no move is like from here for anoth month yet . Attend HQ . dinner . They had the barn tast decor and all the mademoisell of the villag were wait on the tabl . Rode over to Bde , dine in their mess and made a coupl of speech .
